对于两个[[协变张量]]$$a_{i_1,i_2,\cdots,i_\mu}$$和$$b_{i_1,i_2,\cdots,i_\nu}$$，它们的乘积为
$$
(a\otimes{}b)_{i_1,i_2,\cdots,i_{\mu+\nu}}=a_{i_1,i_2,\cdots,i_\mu}b_{i_{\mu+1},i_{\mu+2},\cdots,i_{\mu+\nu}}
$$
